 Klank's visor lit up. "Yes klank smash." His 5 plasma
guns two machine guns and 3 rocket heat seeking
launchers came outt of his sides. "Klank smash."
Guiledart hit him all the compartments went back in.
"Not yet." He looked at Cyngar. "I will stay  here and
look after the base as in case of problems." He
motioned to the com system. "Isnt it about time we
call the preds?"
